    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with documented rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under lateral load. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, offering the precise feedback and mechanical grip characteristic of the M-chassis. While showing minor aesthetic wear, the drivetrain is mechanically sound with a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
