    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been super well-loved and is in great shape for its next owner. It runs smooth, looks sharp, and has plenty of life left for those weekend getaways or daily commutes. It\u2019s been a joy to drive, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
